annotationA: Ribosomal protein S15, isoform A; Structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uS19 family
annotationB: 60S acidic ribosomal protein P2; Plays an important role in the elongation step of protein synthesis
